Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的假日是從給小鳥餵食開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是去慢跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.57,0:01:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可燃垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可回收垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回家沖澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時最後一步是打掃房間和吃早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}(小千 綾音來家裡玩)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小千和綾音來家裡玩的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:57.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H708EC6&\be10}第17話 休息日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是爽子的朋友來玩的日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.19,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去開門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良少女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爽子一模一...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒禮貌的傢伙 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子的朋友...嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子倒是很有禮貌 就是妝太濃
